summary: Something Peter Parker absolutely would do:
body:
Something Peter Parker absolutely would do:

Perform the Stand Out sequence that Max Goof does from the Goofy Movie at school in the Spider-Man costume to impress Liz/ MJ/ whoever then webslings himself out a window so that he doesn’t get caught.

He also webshoots Dash in the face “on accident” because he saw the opportunity and he took it while trapezing all over the assembly hall.

Thank you and welcome to my TedTalk
